Red Trust/Negative trust account is not allowed to join our campaign.11. Submit your weekly report on this thread before deadline.I'm a bounty Manager from Blank-Head-HR. My duty is manage bounties. I'm not any part of this project team so reward distribution is all upto team. We're not responsible for project success. If you're agreed this rules you can join at your own risk. Follow BitStore official Twitter Page.2.You should have minimum 1000 followers on twitter.3. Your twiiter auditscore must minimum 90%.4.Minimum 10 retweet & 10 tweet per week maximum 30.5. Your tweet should have their farming & staking informations screenshot , Their Tokenomics Screenshots or Current Prize of Bitstore Token. 6. Don't spam same tweet everyday otherwise you won't get stakes make it organic.7. Must join their official telegram group & our Bounty group.8. Use information from official social networks.
